  <title translate="true">Generating and Editing Meshes</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Generating and Editing Meshes</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Meshes are used in SUTRA models. Meshes can be generated in several ways.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The mesh location and element size can be specified by objects which are then used to create an irregular mesh.</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The user can </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Using_Objects_to_Specify_the_M" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">use objects to define where the mesh should be</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and the mesh element size then use the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Mesh|Generate Mesh...</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> command to create it.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The user can can </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Using_Fishnet_Mesh_Quadrilater" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">draw fishnet-mesh quadrilaterals</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> which will then be subdivided to create the mesh.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The user can draw individual elements either to </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Editing_a_Mesh" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">modify an existing mesh or to create an entire mesh</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></li>
    </list>
  </body>
</topic>
